OL,3,CChildren's home boss sexually abused
OL,4,Cboys and girls over two decades
OL,6,FA children's home manager used his
OL,7,F"unfettered access" to vulnerable
OL,8,Fyoungsters to sexually abuse boys and
OL,9,Fgirls in his care for almost two
OL,10,Fdecades, a jury has found.
OL,12,FMalcolm Phillips used children "for
OL,13,Fhis own sexual gratification" during
OL,14,Fhis 18-year regime of fear at Skircoat
OL,15,FLodge Care Home in Halifax, West
OL,16,FYorkshire.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@SO]tD@`OUuD@]O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/14
