PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1771952662
OL,3,CChildren's home boss sexually abused
OL,4,Cboys and girls over two decades
OL,6,FOn Monday 23 February, a jury at
OL,7,FBradford Crown Court found that
OL,8,FPhillips had committed sexual offences
OL,9,Fagainst six victims ` four female and
OL,10,Ftwo male ` between 1976 and 1994.
OL,12,FPhillips, who is now 93 years old, was
OL,13,Ffound unfit to stand trial, so a trial-
OL,14,Fof-facts was held in which jurors were
OL,15,Fasked to determine whether or not he
OL,16,Fhad committed the acts alleged.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1771952662
OL,3,CChildren's home boss sexually abused
OL,4,Cboys and girls over two decades
OL,6,FHis assistant, Linda Brunning, 66, was
OL,7,Ffound guilty of restraining one boy
OL,8,Fwhile Phillips sexually assaulted him
OL,9,Fand indecently assaulting another
OL,10,Fherself while drying him after a
OL,11,Fshower.
OL,13,FBrunning put her head in her hands and
OL,14,Fstarted to sob when the verdicts were
OL,15,Fread out. Phillips was not in court.
OL,17,FIt was Phillips's second prosecution
OL,18,Fover abuse at Skircoat Lodge, after he
OL,19,Fwas jailed in 2001 for sexual offences
OL,20,Fagainst eight female residents.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
