FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1771952662
OL,3,CChildren's home boss sexually abused
OL,4,Cboys and girls over two decades
OL,6,FProsecutors said abuse at the home
OL,7,Fwent "unfettered and unreported
OL,8,Fagainst a backdrop of legitimacy" for
OL,9,Falmost 20 years.
OL,11,FJurors heard how female complainants,
OL,12,Fwho were told to wear nighties for
OL,13,Fbed, described Phillips coming into
OL,14,Ftheir bedrooms at night and indecently
OL,15,Fassaulting them.
OL,26,@oD@FOUpD@aO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1771952662
OL,3,CChildren's home boss sexually abused
OL,4,Cboys and girls over two decades
OL,6,FOpening the trial in January,
OL,7,Fprosecutor Michelle Colborne KC said
OL,8,FPhillips controlled Skircoat Lodge and
OL,9,Flived in a flat leading to the girls'
OL,10,Fbedrooms, which gave him "unfettered
OL,11,Faccess".
OL,13,F"During the course of almost two
OL,14,Fdecades, Malcolm Phillips used his
OL,15,Fpower to isolate specific children to
OL,16,Fuse for his sexual gratification, and
OL,17,Fhe wasn't the only one," she told
OL,18,Fjurors.
OL,26,@rD@ZOUsD@GO]uD@AOUyD@XO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1771952662
OL,3,CChildren's home boss sexually abused
OL,4,Cboys and girls over two decades
OL,6,FThe court heard Brunning, who worked
OL,7,Falongside Phillips for 16 years, was
OL,8,Falso "adept at isolating and
OL,9,Fmanipulating children".
OL,11,FMs Colborne said Brunning was "a large
OL,12,Fand domineering woman who took
OL,13,Fpleasure in physically hurting and
OL,14,Fhumiliating children".
OL,16,F"At times she would perform sexual
OL,17,Fassaults on them, at her worst she
OL,18,Ffacilitated the abuse by Malcolm
OL,19,FPhillips upon a small defenceless
OL,20,Fchild," she told the court.
OL,26,@pD@FOUqD@VO]sD@_OUvD@UO]xD@AOU|D@GO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1771952662
OL,3,CChildren's home boss sexually abused
OL,4,Cboys and girls over two decades
OL,6,FThe prosecutor said the children were
OL,7,Fchosen carefully by the defendants,
OL,8,Fwho had access to their files and knew
OL,9,Fwhich children could be manipulated.
OL,11,F"They told them no-one cared about
OL,12,Fthem, they told them no-one would
OL,13,Fbelieve them," Ms Colborne said.
OL,15,F"If they ran away from Skircoat Lodge,
OL,16,Fthey were taken straight back by
OL,17,Fpolice, accused of being
OL,18,Ftroublemakers."
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@NO]wD@AOUzD@OO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
