OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1771952662
OL,3,CChildren's home boss sexually abused
OL,4,Cboys and girls over two decades
OL,6,FThe court heard the first complainant,
OL,7,Fwho was sent to Skircoat Lodge as a
OL,8,Fteenager in the late 1970s, remembered
OL,9,Fthat girls were told to "wear nighties
OL,10,Fto bed".
OL,12,F"While in bed, while the lights were
OL,13,Fout, she would hear Phillips enter the
OL,14,Fbedroom, he would approach her bed and
OL,15,Ftouch her under her nightie", Ms
OL,16,FColborne said.
OL,18,FThe court heard the girl started
OL,19,Frunning away but was always taken back
OL,20,Fby police, with the home branding her
OL,21,F"an accomplished liar".
OL,26,@qD@YOUrD@GO]tD@AOUwD@\O]}D@AOU}D@VO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1771952662
OL,3,CChildren's home boss sexually abused
OL,4,Cboys and girls over two decades
OL,6,FMs Colborne said the second
OL,7,Fcomplainant, who was 10 years old at
OL,8,Fthe time, accused Phillips of sexually
OL,9,Fassaulting her on at least 10
OL,10,Foccasions while she was in bed.
OL,12,FThe court heard Phillips "seemed to
OL,13,Fhave taken her under his wing and
OL,14,Freferred to her as one of his special
OL,15,Fgirls".
OL,17,FBoth Phillips and Brunning were found
OL,18,Fto have indecently assaulted the third
OL,19,Fcomplainant, a 14-year-old boy, while
OL,20,Fdrying him after a shower on at least
OL,21,Ftwo occasions.
OL,26,@tD@ZOUwD@FO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
