PN,36510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1771952662
OL,3,CChildren's home boss sexually abused
OL,4,Cboys and girls over two decades
OL,6,FBrunning was also found guilty of
OL,7,Frestraining the fourth complainant, a
OL,8,Fboy aged between nine and 13, while
OL,9,FPhillips sexually assaulted him in the
OL,10,Fbathroom, on numerous occasions.
OL,12,FThe court heard the boy started to run
OL,13,Faway because of the abuse he suffered
OL,14,Ffrom Phillips and Brunning, but was
OL,15,Ftaken back every time and punished by
OL,16,Fthe two defendants, who dunked him in
OL,17,Fa bath of cold water.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
