FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1771952662
OL,3,CChildren's home boss sexually abused
OL,4,Cboys and girls over two decades
OL,6,FJurors found Phillips raped the fifth
OL,7,Fcomplainant twice. They heard she was
OL,8,Fplaced at Skircoat Lodge as a teenager
OL,9,Fand "couldn't believe she had been
OL,10,Fraped in the place she was sent to for
OL,11,Fsafety".
OL,13,FHe was also found to have indecently
OL,14,Fassaulted the sixth complainant, a
OL,15,Fgirl aged between 11 and 12, on at
OL,16,Fleast three occasions, after inviting
OL,17,Fher into his office to do homework.
OL,19,FMs Colborne said Phillips would give
OL,20,Fthe girl a lollipop afterwards.
OL,26,@qD@EOUsD@GO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1771952662
OL,3,CChildren's home boss sexually abused
OL,4,Cboys and girls over two decades
OL,6,FThe court heard Phillips's "regime of
OL,7,Ffear" at the home came to an end when
OL,8,Fhe was suspended in 1994 after an
OL,9,Finvestigation.
OL,11,FIn a statement to police in 2019, he
OL,12,Fsaid the victims were liars and that
OL,13,Fhe had been the victim of a high-
OL,14,Fprofile media campaign to discredit
OL,15,Fhim.
OL,17,FGiving evidence during the trial,
OL,18,FBrunning denied having a sexual
OL,19,Finterest in children and said she felt
OL,20,F"sick" when she was told about the
OL,21,Fallegations against her.
OL,26,@nD@\OUoD@EO]|D@AOU|D@FO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G12/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1771952662
OL,3,CChildren's home boss sexually abused
OL,4,Cboys and girls over two decades
OL,6,FThe jury found Phillips, of Tyseley,
OL,7,FBirmingham, had committed three counts
OL,8,Fof indecent assault, two counts of
OL,9,Findecency with a child, three counts
OL,10,Fof indecent assault on a male person,
OL,11,Ftwo counts of buggery and two of rape.
OL,13,FBrunning, of Sowerby Bridge, near
OL,14,FHalifax, was found guilty of two
OL,15,Fcounts of aiding and abetting indecent
OL,16,Fassault, two of aiding and abetting
OL,17,Fbuggery and one of indecent assault.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G13/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
