FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1771952662
OL,3,CChildren's home boss sexually abused
OL,4,Cboys and girls over two decades
OL,6,FBrunning was remanded in custody until
OL,7,Fsentencing on April 27, when Judge
OL,8,FKirstie Watson said she would
OL,9,F"inevitably" receive a jail sentence.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G14/14
